      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MCIVOR MORGAN (1) jumps from the inside draw. Last start finished 6th over 300m at this track beaten 2.5 lengths (17.22) behind Glamorous Jewel in a Grade 5 on June 5. Looks a key player on best form. WHY NOT ZACH (3) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by half a length at Warragul in a handy 23.09 beating Rapidfire Layla. Has a low draw and in form and has the ability. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Deserves serious consideration again. SNAG (2) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at this track over 300m (17.11). Shapes as one to consider. SAILOR SONG (5) is in winning form and worth including in the main hopes.",
